Ingredients:

For the Halušky (Potato Dumplings):

4 large potatoes, peeled and grated
2 cups all-purpose flour
1 egg
Salt to taste

For the Bryndzové (Cheese Sauce):

1 cup Bryndza cheese (or a mixture of feta and cream cheese as a substitute)
1/2 cup sour cream
4 tablespoons unsalted butter
Salt and black pepper to taste


For Garnish:

Cooked and crumbled bacon (optional)
Chopped chives or green onions (optional)
